♪This love was never easy♪

894
00:39:54,940 --> 00:39:59,100
♪So I believe without doubt♪

895
00:39:59,740 --> 00:40:02,340
♪Like a thousand sails passing by♪

896
00:40:02,340 --> 00:40:07,260
♪Reaching shore
at the first light of dawn♪

897
00:40:07,740 --> 00:40:09,620
♪This bond will never waver♪

898
00:40:09,620 --> 00:40:14,620
♪So joy and sorrow
